# Stock Portfolio Tracker - Project Report

## Overview
A Python-based application to track stock investments with real-time data from financial APIs.

## Features Implemented
- Add/remove stocks from portfolio
- Track current prices using Alpha Vantage API
- Calculate portfolio value and performance
- Basic command-line interface

## Technical Details
- Python 3.x
- Requests library for API calls
- Object-oriented design
- Modular architecture

## Setup Instructions
1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies: `pip install -r requirements.txt`
3. Get API key from Alpha Vantage
4. Run: `python app/main.py`

